creator: NABU.ORG
descriptionHtml:
NABU.ORG is a free reading application for children and adults. This app is free to download on Android devices, such as mobile phones and tablets.

Our collection of books features early grade reading books, fiction and non-fiction stories, educational materials, and more. Books are available in English and Kinyarwanda, and they are published by Rwandan publishers and international publishers.

NABU.ORG’s collection is appropriate for early childhood readers, primary and secondary students, University students, and adults.

Local Rwandan publishers featured in the app include: Longhorn Publishers, African Storybook Project, and more!

title: NABU.ORG

creator: NABU.ORG
descriptionHtml:
NABU.ORG is a free and easy to use reading application for children and adults. This app is free to download on Android devices, such as mobile phones and tablets.

NABU creates early grade reading books that allow children to see themselves and the world they live in reflected in the stories. Our collection of books features fiction and non-fiction stories, educational materials, and more. The books have been published by both local and international publishers, and are available in a variety of languages including English, Kiswahili, Kinyarwanda, French, Cebuano, Kreyol and, Filipino.

NABU.ORG’s collection is bilingual and is a great resource for early childhood readers, primary school students, teachers, and parents. Bilingual books are essentials to inclusive and equitable learning.

NABU makes mother tongue stories that help children succeed. Read hundreds of bilingual children's stories created by local authors and illustrators on your mobile device now!

Local publishers featured in the app include Longhorn Publishers, African Storybook Project, and more!
descriptionShort: NABU.ORG is a free reading application for children and adults

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Version 2.0 of the NABU app is a completely redesigned experience. Changes include: children’s profiles, social login, language localization (Kinyarwanda, Haitian Creole, Swahili, Tagalog, French), push notifications, speed enhancements.

title: NABU.ORG

creator: NABU.ORG
descriptionHtml:
NABU brings the wonder of reading to children, with free and fun multilingual stories levelled to the child's reading ability. Bilingual, mother tongue books help children to learn and grow.

The NABU App is easy to use - by creating your children's individual profile you can customise it to your child's reading level and search and browse for books in different categories.

The bilingual, mother tongue books are available in English, Swahili, French and Kinyarwanda and once downloaded can be read offline.

Bond with your child and students through the love of reading culturally relevant stories even adults can enjoy! It's never too early to start reading with your child.
descriptionShort: The leading app bringing the wonder of reading right to your child’s fingertips.

creator: NABU.ORG
descriptionHtml:
NABU, the leading mother tongue children’s app, brings the wonder of reading to your child.
NABU is a world of free culturally relevant, mother-tongue storybooks for kids, designed to inspire reading and learning. With books in 28+ languages, personalized recommendations, fun quizzes, and a friendly mascot to guide their journey, kids can explore, learn, and grow. From bilingual learning to grade-level assessments, NABU equips children with tools to succeed while sparking joy and curiosity. Ideal for parents, teachers, and kids who dream big. Join us in our mission to eradicate illiteracy and unlock every child’s potential.
descriptionShort: Ignite a love for reading with free books in 28+ languages

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What’s New in NABU App!
We’ve made exciting updates to enhance your child’s literacy journey:
• Personalized Profiles: Customize profiles with ease.
• Grade-Level Assessments: Tailored recommendations for every learner.
• Smart Book Suggestions: Find books by language, level, and topics.
• Interactive Assessments: Track progress with quizzes and scores.
• Mascot Fun!: Get tips and playful reactions during quizzes.
Update now!
